scatter_doe_produce_plot <- function(mizr_df, labels_vec, fac_vec, response_var, mean_val,

                    		
                  

                  

                    196
                    
                    
                      
                                     sd_df = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    197
                    
                    
                      
                                     treatment_fac = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    198
                    
                    
                      
                                     doe_plot_style = "enhanced") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    199
                    
                    
                      
  #' Produces a scatter plot that colors and shapes by the treatment factor

                    		
                  

                  

                    200
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param mizr_df the data frame

                    		
                  

                  

                    201
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param labels_vec the vector names of the labels

                    		
                  

                  

                    202
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param fac_vec the factors to plot on the x column

                    		
                  

                  

                    203
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param response_var the response variable to plot on the y axis

                    		
                  

                  

                    204
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param mean_val the mean value

                    		
                  

                  

                    205
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param treatment_fac the treatment factor. NULL if none.

                    		
                  

                  

                    206
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param doe_plot_style Specifies the Plot Style. Use "plain" to mimic the DOE Scatter Plot

                    		
                  

                  

                    207
                    
                    
                      
  #' in dataplot, and "enhanced" to use an enhanced version, and

                    		
                  

                  

                    208
                    
                    
                      
  #' "boxplot" to place the boxplot in front of the points, and "sd" to replace the boxplot

                    		
                  

                  

                    209
                    
                    
                      
  #' To produce a mean and standard deviation rather than quantiles. Defaults to "enhanced".

                    		
                  

                  

                    210
                    
                    
                      
  #' @return plot_obj the plot object

                    		
                  

                  

                    211
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    212
                    !
                    
                      
  val_fac_var <- "value_fac"

                    		
                  

                  

                    213
                    !
                    
                      
  val_var <- "value"

                    		
                  

                  

                    214
                    !
                    
                      
  mean_var <- "mean"

                    		
                  

                  

                    215
                    !
                    
                      
  upper_var <- "upper"

                    		
                  

                  

                    216
                    !
                    
                      
  lower_var <- "lower"

                    		
                  

                  

                    217
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    218
                    !
                    
                      
  y_unit <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    219
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    220
                    
                    
                      
  # x-axis jutter for easier viewing of multiple points

                    		
                  

                  

                    221
                    !
                    
                      
  jitter_pos <- position_jitter(width = 0.0, height = 0)

                    		
                  

                  

                    222
                    !
                    
                      
  jitter_dodge_pos <- position_jitterdodge(

                    		
                  

                  

                    223
                    !
                    
                      
    jitter.width = 0.0, jitter.height = 0,

                    		
                  

                  

                    224
                    !
                    
                      
    dodge.width = 0.9

                    		
                  

                  

                    225
                    
                    
                      
  )

                    		
                  

                  

                    226
                    !
                    
                      
  boxplot_dodge_pos <- position_dodge(width = 0.9)

                    		
                  

                  

                    227
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    228
                    !
                    
                      
  plot_obj <- ggplot(data = mizr_df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    229
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    230
                    !
                    
                      
  if (doe_plot_style == "plain") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    231
                    
                    
                      
    # Treatment factor is not used in the plain dataplot style

                    		
                  

                  

                    232
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj +

                    		
                  

                  

                    233
                    !
                    
                      
      geom_hline(yintercept = mean_val, lwd = 0.6, color = "gray50", linetype = "dashed") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    234
                    !
                    
                      
      geom_point(aes_string(x = val_fac_var, y = response_var, group = 1),

                    		
                  

                  

                    235
                    !
                    
                      
        size = 4

                    		
                  

                  

                    236
                    
                    
                      
      ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    237
                    !
                    
                      
      geom_path(aes_string(x = val_fac_var, y = response_var, group = val_var),

                    		
                  

                  

                    238
                    !
                    
                      
        linetype = "solid"

                    		
                  

                  

                    239
                    
                    
                      
      ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    240
                    !
                    
                      
      scale_x_discrete(breaks = unique(mizr_df$value_fac), labels = labels_vec) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    241
                    !
                    
                      
      facet_grid(. ~ variable, scales = "free_x", switch = "x") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    242
                    !
                    
                      
      scale_color_discrete(guide = FALSE) + xlab("Factor") + ylab(response_var) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    243
                    !
                    
                      
      ggtitle("DOE Scatter Plot (Dataplot Style)") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    244
                    !
                    
                      
      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    245
                    !
                    
                      
  } else if (doe_plot_style == "boxplot") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    246
                    !
                    
                      
    if (is.null(treatment_fac)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    247
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_obj <- plot_obj +

                    		
                  

                  

                    248
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_vline(

                    		
                  

                  

                    249
                    !
                    
                      
          xintercept = seq(1.5, length(unique(mizr_df$val_name)) - 0.5, 1), lwd = 0.4,

                    		
                  

                  

                    250
                    !
                    
                      
          color = "gray50", linetype = 2

                    		
                  

                  

                    251
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    252
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_boxplot(aes_string(x = val_fac_var, y = response_var, group = val_var),

                    		
                  

                  

                    253
                    !
                    
                      
          width = 0.6,

                    		
                  

                  

                    254
                    !
                    
                      
          alpha = 0.8

                    		
                  

                  

                    255
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    256
                    !
                    
                      
        scale_x_discrete(breaks = unique(mizr_df$value_fac), labels = labels_vec) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    257
                    !
                    
                      
        facet_grid(. ~ variable, scales = "free_x", switch = "x") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    258
                    !
                    
                      
        scale_color_discrete(guide = FALSE) + xlab("Factor") + ylab(response_var) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    259
                    !
                    
                      
        ggtitle("DOE-Style Scatter Plot (Boxplot at Front)") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    260
                    !
                    
                      
        guides(alpha = FALSE) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    261
                    !
                    
                      
        theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    262
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    263
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_obj <- plot_obj +

                    		
                  

                  

                    264
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_vline(

                    		
                  

                  

                    265
                    !
                    
                      
          xintercept = seq(1.5, length(unique(mizr_df$val_name)) - 0.5, 1), lwd = 0.4,

                    		
                  

                  

                    266
                    !
                    
                      
          color = "gray50", linetype = 2

                    		
                  

                  

                    267
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    268
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_boxplot(

                    		
                  

                  

                    269
                    !
                    
                      
          aes_string(

                    		
                  

                  

                    270
                    !
                    
                      
            x = val_fac_var, y = response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    271
                    !
                    
                      
            color = treatment_fac

                    		
                  

                  

                    272
                    
                    
                      
          ),

                    		
                  

                  

                    273
                    !
                    
                      
          width = 0.6, alpha = 0.8,

                    		
                  

                  

                    274
                    !
                    
                      
          outlier.shape = treatment_fac, position = boxplot_dodge_pos

                    		
                  

                  

                    275
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    276
                    !
                    
                      
        scale_x_discrete(breaks = unique(mizr_df$value_fac), labels = labels_vec) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    277
                    !
                    
                      
        facet_grid(. ~ variable, scales = "free_x", switch = "x") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    278
                    !
                    
                      
        xlab("Factor") + ylab(response_var) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    279
                    !
                    
                      
        ggtitle(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    280
                    !
                    
                      
          "DOE-Style Scatter Plot (Boxplot at Front),\nTreatment Factor ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    281
                    !
                    
                      
          treatment_fac

                    		
                  

                  

                    282
                    
                    
                      
        )) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    283
                    !
                    
                      
        guides(alpha = FALSE) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    284
                    !
                    
                      
        theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    285
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    286
                    !
                    
                      
  } else if (doe_plot_style == "boxplot_points") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    287
                    !
                    
                      
    if (is.null(treatment_fac)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    288
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_obj <- plot_obj +

                    		
                  

                  

                    289
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_vline(

                    		
                  

                  

                    290
                    !
                    
                      
          xintercept = seq(1.5, length(unique(mizr_df$val_name)) - 0.5, 1), lwd = 0.4,

                    		
                  

                  

                    291
                    !
                    
                      
          color = "gray50", linetype = 2

                    		
                  

                  

                    292
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    293
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_hline(yintercept = mean_val, lwd = 0.6, color = "gray50", linetype = "solid") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    294
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_point(aes_string(x = val_fac_var, y = response_var, group = 1),

                    		
                  

                  

                    295
                    !
                    
                      
          size = 4, position = jitter_pos, alpha = 0.8

                    		
                  

                  

                    296
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    297
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_boxplot(aes_string(x = val_fac_var, y = response_var, group = val_var),

                    		
                  

                  

                    298
                    !
                    
                      
          width = 0.6,

                    		
                  

                  

                    299
                    !
                    
                      
          outlier.shape = NA, alpha = 0.8

                    		
                  

                  

                    300
                    
                    
                      
        ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    301
                    !
                    
                      
        scale_x_discrete(breaks = unique(mizr_df$value_fac), labels = labels_vec) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    302
                    !
                    
                      
        facet_grid(. ~ variable, scales = "free_x", switch = "x") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    303
                    !
                    
                      
        scale_color_discrete(guide = FALSE) + xlab("Factor") + ylab(response_var) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    304
                    !
                    
                      
        ggtitle("DOE-Style Scatter Plot (Boxplot at Front)") +

                    		
                  

                  

                    305
                    !
                    
                      
        guides(alpha = FALSE) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    306
                    !
                    
                      
        theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    307
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    308
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_obj <- plot_obj +

                    		
                  

                  

                    309
                    !
                    
                      
        geom_vline(

                    		
                  

                  

                    310
                    !
                    
                      
          xintercept = seq(1.5, length(unique(mizr_df$val_name)) - 0.5, 1), lwd = 0.4,

                    472
                    
                    
                      
scatter_effect_compute_df <- function(df, x_var, response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    473
                    
                    
                      
                                      comp_func = mean, ...) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    474
                    !
                    
                      
  if (length(list(...)) == 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    475
                    !
                    
                      
    effect_df <- aggregate(reformulate(x_var, response_var), df, FUN = comp_func, na.rm = TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    476
                    
                    
                      
  } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    477
                    !
                    
                      
    effect_df <- aggregate(reformulate(x_var, response_var), df, FUN = comp_func, ...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    478
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    479
                    !
                    
                      
  return(effect_df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    480
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    481
                    
                    
                      
scatter_effect_produce_plot <- function(effect_df, x_var, response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    482
                    
                    
                      
                                        comp_func = mean, ...) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    483
                    
                    
                      
  #' Produces a scatter plot that does a main effect of x_var by response_var

                    		
                  

                  

                    484
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param effect_df the data frame

                    		
                  

                  

                    485
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param x_var the factor to plot on the x column

                    		
                  

                  

                    486
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param response_var the response variable to plot on the y axis

                    		
                  

                  

                    487
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param comp_func mean by defalut. The computation function used to aggregate multiple values

                    		
                  

                  

                    488
                    
                    
                      
  #' into a single value

                    		
                  

                  

                    489
                    
                    
                      
  #' @return plot_obj the plot object

                    		
                  

                  

                    490
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    491
                    !
                    
                      
  x_unit <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    492
                    !
                    
                      
  y_unit <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    493
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    494
                    !
                    
                      
  plot_obj <- ggplot(data = effect_df) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    495
                    !
                    
                      
    geom_point(aes_string(x = x_var, y = response_var),

                    		
                  

                  

                    496
                    !
                    
                      
      group = 1

                    		
                  

                  

                    497
                    
                    
                      
    ) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    498
                    !
                    
                      
    geom_line(aes_string(x = x_var, y = response_var), group = 1) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    499
                    !
                    
                      
    ggtitle(paste0("Margins Effect Plot of \nx: ", x_var, ", y: ", response_var)) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    500
                    !
                    
                      
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    501
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    502
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    503
                    !
                    
                      
  if (x_unit != "") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    504
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + xlab(paste0(x_var, " (", x_unit, ")"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    505
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    506
                    !
                    
                      
  if (y_unit != "") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    507
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + ylab(paste0(response_var, " (", y_unit, ")"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    508
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    509
                    !
                    
                      
  return(plot_obj)

                    		
                  

                  

                    510
                    
                    
                      
}

                    517
                    
                    
                      
scatter_treatment_produce_plot <- function(df, x_var, treatment_fac, response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    518
                    
                    
                      
                                           shape_style = "point") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    519
                    
                    
                      
  #' Produces a scatter plot that colors and shapes by the treatment factor

                    		
                  

                  

                    520
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param df the data frame

                    		
                  

                  

                    521
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param x_var the factor to plot on the x column

                    		
                  

                  

                    522
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param treatment_fac the treatment factor

                    		
                  

                  

                    523
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param response_var the response variable to plot on the y axis

                    		
                  

                  

                    524
                    
                    
                      
  #' @param shape_style a string indicating if the shape should be points ('point') or textual

                    		
                  

                  

                    525
                    
                    
                      
  #' symbols 'text'. Defaults to point.

                    		
                  

                  

                    526
                    
                    
                      
  #' @return plot_obj the plot object

                    		
                  

                  

                    527
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    528
                    !
                    
                      
  x_unit <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    529
                    !
                    
                      
  y_unit <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    530
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    531
                    !
                    
                      
  full_var <- "full_label"

                    		
                  

                  

                    532
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    533
                    !
                    
                      
  var_key <- unique(df[[treatment_fac]])

                    		
                  

                  

                    534
                    !
                    
                      
  geom_text_object <- get_custom_text_object(var_key,

                    		
                  

                  

                    535
                    !
                    
                      
    cols = scales::hue_pal()(length(var_key))

                    		
                  

                  

                    536
                    
                    
                      
  )

                    		
                  

                  

                    537
                    !
                    
                      
  plot_obj <- ggplot(data = df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    538
                    !
                    
                      
  if (shape_style == "text") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    539
                    
                    
                      
    # No metadata, use original values as labels

                    		
                  

                  

                    540
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + geom_text_custom(

                    		
                  

                  

                    541
                    !
                    
                      
      aes_string(

                    		
                  

                  

                    542
                    !
                    
                      
        x = x_var, y = response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    543
                    !
                    
                      
        color = treatment_fac, label = treatment_fac

                    		
                  

                  

                    544
                    
                    
                      
      ),

                    		
                  

                  

                    545
                    !
                    
                      
      geom = geom_text_object

                    		
                  

                  

                    546
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    547
                    
                    
                      
  } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    548
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + geom_point(aes_string(

                    		
                  

                  

                    549
                    !
                    
                      
      x = x_var, y = response_var,

                    		
                  

                  

                    550
                    !
                    
                      
      color = treatment_fac

                    		
                  

                  

                    551
                    
                    
                      
    ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    552
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    553
                    !
                    
                      
  plot_obj <- plot_obj + ggtitle(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    554
                    !
                    
                      
    "Scatter plot of x: ", x_var, ", to y: ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    555
                    !
                    
                      
    response_var, "\nwith treatment: ", treatment_fac

                    		
                  

                  

                    556
                    
                    
                      
  )) +

                    		
                  

                  

                    557
                    !
                    
                      
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5))

                    		
                  

                  

                    558
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    559
                    !
                    
                      
  if (x_unit != "") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    560
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + xlab(paste0(x_var, " (", x_unit, ")"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    561
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    562
                    !
                    
                      
  if (y_unit != "") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    563
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_obj <- plot_obj + ylab(paste0(response_var, " (", y_unit, ")"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    564
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    565
                    !
                    
                      
  return(plot_obj)

                    		
                  

                  

                    566
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                
              

            

            

              

                
                  

                    1
                    
                    
                      
penalize_missing <- function(df, score_col, key_col, key_values, dec_col) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    !
                    
                      
  pen_df <- df

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    !
                    
                      
  neg_key_value <- key_values[1]

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    !
                    
                      
  pos_key_value <- key_values[2]

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
  # Add decision of `t` and score of 9999 for nontarget trials

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    !
                    
                      
  if (nrow(pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) & (pen_df[[key_col]] == neg_key_value), ]) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    !
                    
                      
    if (!is.null(dec_col)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    !
                    
                      
      pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) &

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    !
                    
                      
        (pen_df[[key_col]] == neg_key_value), ][[dec_col]] <- pos_key_value

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    !
                    
                      
    pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) &

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    !
                    
                      
      (pen_df[[key_col]] == neg_key_value), ][[score_col]] <- 9999

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      
  # Add decision of `f` and score of -9999 for target trials

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    !
                    
                      
  if (nrow(pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) & (pen_df[[key_col]] == pos_key_value), ]) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    !
                    
                      
    if (!is.null(dec_col)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    18
                    !
                    
                      
      pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) &

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    !
                    
                      
        (pen_df[[key_col]] == pos_key_value), ][[dec_col]] <- neg_key_value

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
                    !
                    
                      
    pen_df[(is.na(pen_df[[score_col]])) &

                    		
                  

                  

                    22
                    !
                    
                      
      (pen_df[[key_col]] == pos_key_value), ][[score_col]] <- -9999

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    !
                    
                      
  return(pen_df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    
                    
                      
get_decision_thresholds <- function(df, score_col, key_col, key_values, dec_col) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    !
                    
                      
  neg_key_value <- key_values[1]

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    !
                    
                      
  pos_key_value <- key_values[2]

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
  # max_t is not used so it is not computed

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    !
                    
                      
  min_f <- min(df[df[[dec_col]] == neg_key_value, score_col])

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    !
                    
                      
  min_t <- min(df[df[[dec_col]] == pos_key_value, score_col])

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    !
                    
                      
  max_f <- max(df[df[[dec_col]] == neg_key_value, score_col])

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    !
                    
                      
  dec_thresh <- 0

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    !
                    
                      
  if (is.na(min_t)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    !
                    
                      
    print(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    !
                    
                      
      "All points are ", neg_key_value,

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    !
                    
                      
      ".\nHence, the paragraph with thresholds may be inconsistent."

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      
    ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    !
                    
                      
    dec_thresh <- max_f

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    !
                    
                      
  } else if (is.na(min_f)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    !
                    
                      
    print(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    !
                    
                      
      "All points are ", pos_key_value,

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    !
                    
                      
      ".\nHence, the paragraph with thresholds may be inconsistent."

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
    ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    !
                    
                      
    dec_thresh <- min_t

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
  } else if (min_t < max_f) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    !
                    
                      
    print(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    !
                    
                      
      "The decision is invalid, \nbecause it is not equivalent to picking a threshold.",

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
      "\nHence, the paragraph with thresholds is inconsistent."

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
    ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    !
                    
                      
    dec_thresh <- (min_t + max_f) / 2

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
  } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
    dec_thresh <- (min_t + max_f) / 2

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    !
                    
                      
  return(dec_thresh)

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
get_dcf <- function(miss_rate, fa_rate, c_miss = 1, c_fa = 1, p_hkv = 0.5) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    !
                    
                      
  value <- (c_miss * miss_rate * p_hkv) + (c_fa * fa_rate * (1 - p_hkv))

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
  return(value)

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
compute_dcf_for_det_df <- function(det_df_row, c_miss = 1, c_fa = 1, p_hkv = 0.5) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    !
                    
                      
  miss_rate <- det_df_row[2]

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    !
                    
                      
  fa_rate <- det_df_row[3]

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    !
                    
                      
  dcf_val <- get_dcf(miss_rate, fa_rate, c_miss, c_fa, p_hkv)

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    !
                    
                      
  return(dcf_val)

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
}

tdeviate_trans <- function() {

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    !
                    
                      
  trans_new("tdeviate", qnorm, pnorm)

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    75

# reduce keydf to score, targettype

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      
det_compute_df <- function(df, score_col, key_col, key_values = c(0, 1), dec_col = NULL) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    !
                    
                      
  neg_key_value <- key_values[1]

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    !
                    
                      
  pos_key_value <- key_values[2]

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    !
                    
                      
  pen_df <- penalize_missing(df, score_col, key_col, key_values, dec_col)

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df <- pen_df[, c(score_col, key_col)]

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    !
                    
                      
  names(score_df) <- c("score", "key")

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    !
                    
                      
  threshs <- as.data.frame(table(score_df$score))

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    !
                    
                      
  target_threshs <- as.data.frame(table(score_df[score_df$key == pos_key_value, ]$score))

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    !
                    
                      
  nontarget_threshs <- as.data.frame(table(score_df[score_df$key == neg_key_value, ]$score))

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET <- merge(merge(threshs, target_threshs, by = "Var1", all = TRUE),

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    !
                    
                      
    nontarget_threshs,

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    !
                    
                      
    by = "Var1", all = TRUE

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    
                    
                      
  )

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET[is.na(score_df_DET)] <- 0

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    !
                    
                      
  names(score_df_DET) <- c("score", "new_points", "new_ms", "new_tn")

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$score <- as.numeric(levels(score_df_DET$score))[score_df_DET$score]

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    
                    
                      
  # add first row with 0 new points and score of -Inf

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET <- rbind(c(-Inf, 0, 0, 0), score_df_DET)

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    
                    
                      
  ### First, compute the total number of targets and the total number of points

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    !
                    
                      
  num_targets <- sum(score_df_DET$new_ms)

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    !
                    
                      
  num_non_targets <- sum(score_df_DET$new_tn)

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    !
                    
                      
  num_points <- num_targets + num_non_targets

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    
                    
                      
  ### Now produce the DET Curve

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_ms <- cumsum(score_df_DET$new_ms)

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_tn <- cumsum(score_df_DET$new_tn)

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_condneg <- score_df_DET$num_ms + score_df_DET$num_tn

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_condpos <- num_points - score_df_DET$num_condneg

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_tp <- num_targets - score_df_DET$num_ms

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$num_fa <- score_df_DET$num_condpos - score_df_DET$num_tp

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$total_points <- score_df_DET$num_fa + score_df_DET$num_tn + score_df_DET$num_tp +

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    !
                    
                      
    score_df_DET$num_ms

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
  # now compute det values

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$miss_rate <- score_df_DET$num_ms / num_targets

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    !
                    
                      
  score_df_DET$fa_rate <- score_df_DET$num_fa / num_non_targets

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    !
                    
                      
  return(score_df_DET[, c("score", "miss_rate", "fa_rate")])

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      
det_compute_costs_df <- function(df, det_df, score_col, key_col, key_values, dec_col,

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
                                 cp_miss, cp_fa, pp_hkv,

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    
                    
                      
                                 cs_miss, cs_fa, ps_hkv) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    !
                    
                      
  neg_key_value <- key_values[1]

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    !
                    
                      
  pos_key_value <- key_values[2]

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    !
                    
                      
  det_df$dcf_p <- apply(det_df, 1, FUN = compute_dcf_for_det_df, cp_miss, cp_fa, pp_hkv)

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    !
                    
                      
  det_df$dcf_s <- apply(det_df, 1, FUN = compute_dcf_for_det_df, cs_miss, cs_fa, ps_hkv)

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    !
                    
                      
  min_dcf_p <- min(det_df$dcf_p)

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    !
                    
                      
  min_dcf_row_p <- det_df[det_df$dcf_p == min(det_df$dcf_p), ]

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    !
                    
                      
  min_miss_rate_p <- min_dcf_row_p[, "miss_rate"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    !
                    
                      
  min_fa_rate_p <- min_dcf_row_p[, "fa_rate"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    !
                    
                      
  min_thresh_p <- min_dcf_row_p[, "score"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    !
                    
                      
  min_dcf_s <- min(det_df$dcf_s)

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    !
                    
                      
  min_dcf_row_s <- det_df[det_df$dcf_s == min(det_df$dcf_s), ]

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    !
                    
                      
  min_miss_rate_s <- min_dcf_row_s[, "miss_rate"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    !
                    
                      
  min_fa_rate_s <- min_dcf_row_s[, "fa_rate"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    !
                    
                      
  min_thresh_s <- min_dcf_row_s[, "score"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      
  # Make costs_df with min info

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    !
                    
                      
  act_dcf_p <- NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    !
                    
                      
  act_dcf_s <- NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    !
                    
                      
  act_miss_rate <- NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    !
                    
                      
  act_fa_rate <- NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    !
                    
                      
  act_thresh <- NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    
                    
                      
  # get decision statistics if dec_col is not NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    !
                    
                      
  if (!is.null(dec_col)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    !
                    
                      
    dec_thresh <- get_decision_thresholds(df, score_col, key_col, key_values, dec_col)

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    
                    
                      
    # We select a threshold between a decisions, so the actual threshold is not a row in

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    
                    
                      
    # the det_df

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      
    # Compute actual DCF

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    !
                    
                      
    act_num_tp <- nrow(df[(df[[key_col]] == pos_key_value) & (df[[dec_col]] == pos_key_value), ])

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    !
                    
                      
    act_num_fa <- nrow(df[(df[[key_col]] == neg_key_value) & (df[[dec_col]] == pos_key_value), ])

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    !
                    
                      
    act_num_ms <- nrow(df[(df[[key_col]] == pos_key_value) & (df[[dec_col]] == neg_key_value), ])

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    !
                    
                      
    act_num_tn <- nrow(df[(df[[key_col]] == neg_key_value) & (df[[dec_col]] == neg_key_value), ])

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    !
                    
                      
    act_miss_rate <- act_num_ms / (act_num_ms + act_num_tp)

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    !
                    
                      
    act_fa_rate <- act_num_fa / (act_num_fa + act_num_tn)

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    !
                    
                      
    act_dcf_p <- get_dcf(act_miss_rate, act_fa_rate, cp_miss, cp_fa, pp_hkv)

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    !
                    
                      
    act_dcf_s <- get_dcf(act_miss_rate, act_fa_rate, cs_miss, cs_fa, ps_hkv)

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    !
                    
                      
    act_thresh <- dec_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    !
                    
                      
  costs_df <- data.frame(

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    !
                    
                      
    act_thresh = c(act_thresh), act_miss_rate = c(act_miss_rate),

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    !
                    
                      
    act_fa_rate = c(act_fa_rate), act_dcf_p = c(act_dcf_p),

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    !
                    
                      
    act_dcf_s = c(act_dcf_s),

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    !
                    
                      
    min_thresh_p = c(min_thresh_p),

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    !
                    
                      
    min_miss_rate_p = c(min_miss_rate_p), min_fa_rate_p = c(min_fa_rate_p),

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    !
                    
                      
    min_dcf_p = c(min_dcf_p), min_thresh_s = c(min_thresh_s),

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    !
                    
                      
    min_miss_rate_s = c(min_miss_rate_s), min_fa_rate_s = c(min_fa_rate_s),

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    !
                    
                      
    min_dcf_s = c(min_dcf_s)

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    
                    
                      
  )

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    !
                    
                      
  return(costs_df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    
                    
                      
}

                    		
                  

                  

                    168

                             dec_col, cp_miss, cp_fa, pp_hkv,

  det_plot <- ggplot() +

      color = "System DET", fill = "System DET",

    ), size = 2)

                    !
                    
                      
  if (!is.null(dec_col)) {

    det_plot <- det_plot + geom_point(data = costs_df, aes(

      x = act_fa_rate, y = act_miss_rate,

      color = "act", fill = "act",

    x = min_fa_rate_s, y = min_miss_rate_s,

    color = "min s", fill = "min s",

  det_plot <- det_plot +
